# Trivy suppression policy (Website)
#
# Governance:
# - Every suppressed finding must include: ID, ticket, owner, expiry date.
# - Suppressions require security approval and must be removed by expiry.
# - Keep this file minimal; prefer remediation over suppression.
#
# Example:
# AVD-XXX-YYYY # SEC-1234 owner:jdoe expires:2026-06-30 reason:false-positive
